      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and refined aesthetics. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, offering a balanced combination of performance and long-term reliability. It represents a sophisticated acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a premium automotive experience at an authoritative market value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
