    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver that still looks great cruising down the street. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 29800.0,
